&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.viaduct.ai/&quot;&gt;Viaduct &lt;/a&gt;uses patented AI to discover hidden patterns in complex time series data to reduce the cost of quality management and enable predictive maintenance at scale.&amp;nbsp; Our solution was built to solve the toughest problems in connected asset (passenger vehicles, commercial vehicles, construction equipment, agriculture equipment, etc) AI.&amp;nbsp; We use AI to find meaningful patterns in connected data to aid quality, manufacturing, engineering and after-sales organizations.&amp;nbsp; Viaduct’s differentiation includes patented AI, proprietary infrastructure and domain expertise. Our output includes data unification, early issue detection, significantly faster root-cause analysis and equipment specific service recommendations.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
