&lt;p&gt;The role requires excellent attention to detail, collaboration, communication and organizational skills, paired with the ability to manage multiple projects and customers. Additionally, you are a skilled analytics practitioner who knows how to apply practical data analytics to create solutions that drive measurable impact&lt;/p&gt;
